desc.cn: 为基地供电的大型电源组之一，目前处于损坏状态。
desc.en: One of the large electric generators supplying power to the Base. It is currently damaged.

desc.cn: 一台已经损坏的终端机
desc.en: A broken terminal device.

desc.cn: 观测站的大门开关，里面精巧的源石机关结构似乎已经损坏了
desc.en: The gate switch of the observation post. The intricate Originium components within it seem to be damaged.

desc.cn: ……修好之后，我们还能说它是原来的那套设备吗？
desc.en: If we were to fix this, can this facility still be considered the same as the original?

desc.cn: 这台设备受到了相当程度的破坏，修复它恐怕颇耗资材。
desc.en: This facility has suffered severe damage. Fixing it might cost plenty of materials.

desc.cn: 这台设备受损轻微，使用一点材料即可让它恢复正常。
desc.en: This facility has taken slight damage. You'll just need some materials to restore it to working order.

name.cn: 源石副产物中心的大门

desc.cn: 这台设备的控制装置被人为破坏，缺少了关键的零件。
desc.en: The control apparatus of this machine has been sabotaged. A crucial component is missing.

desc.cn: 这台设备受到了相当程度的破坏，修复它恐怕颇耗资材。
desc.en: This facility has suffered severe damage. Fixing it might cost plenty of materials.

desc.cn: 这是天师坛的启动桩，可将玉键放置在此处来激活天师坛。
desc.en: An activation pillar for the Tianshi Shrine. Place a Jade Key on it to perform the Tianshi Shrine activation process.

desc.cn: 这台设备已经休眠了太久，需要注入足量的息壤才能激活。
desc.en: This facility has been dormant for too long. Inject it with sufficient Xiranite to activate.

desc.cn: 池底废墟大门前的机关，共有三道，只有将三道机关都激活，方可开启大门
desc.en: A mechanism for the main gate of the underwater ruin. There are three of these. All three mechanisms must be activated to open the main gate.

desc.cn: 三到钟的符文组件，需要注入足量的息壤才能激活。
desc.en: A rune for the Bell of Three Presences. Inject it with enough Xiranite to activate it.

desc.cn: 有些陈旧的开关装置。似乎设有特殊的验证机制，或许只能用工团特制的钥匙卡才能开启……
desc.en: A few old switches. Though it seemingly lacks unique verification mechanisms, a special UWST key card might be needed to activate them...
